Kitchen innovation: Vauth Sagel’s new kitchen innovations CORNERSTONE and VSA address unused corner, wasted gaps under your countertop and blind edges that leave no room for accessing cabinets, according to a release from the company.Vauth Sagel’s Cornerstone is a swivelling system component for corner cabinets that automatically extends the entire contents out of the cabinet upon opening the door. And VSA is a solution for opening angles of 90-160°. HÄFELE is the sole distributor.